      "description": "Hey there! I am beyond excited to list this absolute gem. If you're looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in truly mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve treated it like my own baby and it really shows. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom floor. No scratches, no weird smells, just that amazing fresh-car feel. You\u2019ve really gotta see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
