    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 chassis represents the pinnacle of JDM engineering, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six paired with the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission. The vehicle retains its factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential and exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, reflecting its meticulous upkeep. Mechanical integrity is absolute, with no evidence of fluid weeping or heat-cycle fatigue on the OEM intercooler piping. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, offering the precise lateral stability and dampening characteristics expected of a showroom-quality specimen. This is a rare, unmodified example with original VIN tags on all panels and a flawless undercarriage, delivering a visceral, high-fidelity driving experience.",
