      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This single-owner vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and reflects a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected since day one by a full-body ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, with no visible wear on the bolsters or alcantara trim. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a full BMW dealership service history and having never seen a track day or inclement weather. Every button, switch, and electronic system functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a turn-key opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a pristine example of one of the finest driver\u2019s cars ever produced.",
